WEBVTT

26:55.800 --> 26:58.690 line:80%
They paid 3 years of tuition
for that ingrate.

26:58.910 --> 27:01.520 line:80%
One year alone costs 3 taels and 20 mace.

27:01.920 --> 27:04.580 line:80%
Do the math—how much would that be
after 3 years?

27:04.800 --> 27:06.070 line:80%
Nine taels and 60 mace.
